snippet.title: Afro Samurai 2: Revenge of Kuma - Deadly Identities by Visual Eyez Music Video | PS4
snippet.description:
Check out the first official music video for ‘Deadly Identities’, one of the official tracks included in the soon to be released video game Afro Samurai 2.  

Rated Mature: Intense Violence, Blood and Gore, Partial Nudity, Strong Language

http://www.afrosamuraigame.com
